msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:14
msgid ""
"No validation record exists. May be experimental, draft, or community-"
"contributed."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:20
msgid ""
"Badges appear on DMN cards in both the Available DMNs panel and the Chain "
"Composer. Hovering over a badge shows a tooltip with the validating "
"organisation's name and the validation date in Dutch format."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:24
msgid "Data source"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:26
msgid ""
"Validation metadata is stored as RONL Ontology properties on the "
"`cprmv:DecisionModel` resource in TriplyDB and is queried alongside the DMN "
"metadata when the Chain Builder loads. The properties are "
"`ronl:validationStatus`, `ronl:validatedBy`, `ronl:validatedAt`, and "
"optionally `ronl:validationNote`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:28
msgid ""
"Validation metadata is added to a DMN via the CPSV Editor at publish time. "
"See the [CPSV Editor — Publishing to TriplyDB]{1} guide."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:32
msgid "RONL Ontology"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:34
msgid ""
"The governance vocabulary is defined in the RONL Ontology v1.0. For the full "
"property specification, see [CPSV Editor — RONL Ontology]{1}. The LDE-"
"specific properties used for governance badges are documented in [RONL "
"Ontology reference]{2}."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:38
msgid "Backward compatibility"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cgovernance-validation.md:40
msgid ""
"DMN records without validation metadata display normally with no badge. The "
"governance system is purely additive — existing TriplyDB datasets require no "
"changes."
msgstr ""
